uận 10</p>\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/highres_466899254.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-684\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/highres_466899254.png 1098w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/highres_466899254-300x211.png 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/highres_466899254-768x539.png 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/09/highres_466899254-1024x719.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1098px) 100vw, 1098px\" /></figure>\n\n<h2>Tìm speaker</h2>\n\n<p>Như bạn thấy, plan đã có nhưng chưa có speaker, vì vậy mong bạn cùng đóng góp bằng cách đăng ký chủ đề mà bạn muốn nói ở phần comment, hoặc gửi email về địa chỉ: nguyenvanduocit@gmail.com</p>\n\n<h2>Tài trợ</h2>\n\n<p>Xin cảm ơn:</p>\n\n<ul><li>Officience Vietnam đã luôn đồng hành và hỗ trợ địa điểm cho meetup.</li><li>Weglot đã hỗ trợ kinh phí cho thức ăn.</li></ul>\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-3 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4900.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-630\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4900.jpg 3264w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4900-300x225.jpg 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4900-768x576.jpg 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4900-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4900-440x330.jpg 440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3264px) 100vw, 3264px\" /></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img src=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4897.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-629\" srcset=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4897.jpg 3264w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4897-300x225.jpg 300w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4897-768x576.jpg 768w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4897-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://vi.wordpress.org/files/2018/06/IMG_4897-440x330.jpg 440w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 326